// engine's governing-version discipline. Fix per D0123 (accepted): declare `retro` as a Delivery phase
// so the model-driven ceremony filter drops retro gates from actionable (creation-time method
// UNCHANGED); + linkify the review queue (references clickable). EXECUTE. 2 pts.
